    Edit<DispatchStack>

    public abstract class AbstractDispatchLayerEdit
extends Object
implements Edit<DispatchStack>
    Abstraction of an edit acting on a DispatchLayer instance. Handles the check to see that the DispatchLayer supplied is really a DispatchLayerImpl.
